  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK691">
<l>akalā taṇukātu tīkkāyvār pōlka </l>
<l>vikalvēntarc cērntoḻuku vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ministers who serve under fickle-minded monarchs should, like those who warm themselves at the fire, be neither (too) far, nor (too) near.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
